{"tid":950159,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新地委任郭炳湘長子為非執董 連登巴打？","createTime":"2018-12-21T10:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T10:41:30.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4105650e8fc4b9f8e6d7968c66381493e8b8cf25","tid":950159,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:02:01.000Z","msg":"新地（016）宣佈，委任郭炳湘長子郭基俊為新地之非執行董事，該委任自2018年12月21日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n郭基俊現年33歲，於08年5月加入新地，並參與管理新地中港酒店及服務式住宅。他現為集團酒店業務部內之一間附屬公司之董事。郭基俊亦是郭炳湘當年自立門戶創立的帝國集團之董事。<br />\n<br />\n郭基俊作為信託之受益人，他被視為在新地擁有6.46億股的權益，佔新地已發行股份總數22.29%。該等股份中，有7,653萬股股份與郭炳聯、郭基煇、郭基泓及郭顥澧被視為擁有的權益屬相同權益，並重複計算為他們之權益；及有1.27億股股份與郭基煇、郭基泓及郭顥澧被視為擁有的權益屬相同權益，並重複計算為他們之權益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181221/59056298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181221%2F59056298&d=3OQGOEmz9Ym3FKyzYyZMxzACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=fd717731\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181221%2F59056298&h=63303655\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181221/59056298</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181221/large/1545385902_ddfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181221%2Flarge%2F1545385902_ddfe.jpg&h=3f3aac0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一樣款"},{"pid":"1d48eaef7b50fd075fd0bc4bb7823d063c8806a5","tid":950159,"uid":8439,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:09:49.000Z","msg":"如果可以咁有錢我又唔介意咁既樣"},{"pid":"7e1454c645d53356858de1a2a5d39bf5ec3bc8e8","tid":950159,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"NED 可圈可點。好active 又得；俾間房佢齋坐叫天不應又得"}]}